Controller.Cell

Class CellFix

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • Controller.Cell.Cell
          • Controller.Cell.CellFix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class CellFix
extends Cell
    This class represent a cell of our grid, which contain a number between 1 to 9 or nothing, on the window, link the view and the Model package, We cannot change the value on this one.
